 Body Chain\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv data-element-type=\"ParagraphBodyText\" data-element-index=\"1\"\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://nordstrom.sjv.io/c/1141873/1960196/23920?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nordstrom.com%2Fs%2Fslim-belly-chain%2F6954316\u0026amp;subId1=___psv__p_49135775__t_w__r_www.popsugar.com%2Ffashion%2Fbandage-dress-trend-49446365_\u0026amp;subId3=product\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer sponsored\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVIDAKUSH Slim Belly Chain\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e ($75)\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"1\"\u003eAdd a subtle statement to your swim or summer look with this dainty gold chain, which looks really cute paired with a bikini for a fun beach day.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://nordstrom.sjv.io/c/1141873/1960196/23920?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nordstrom.com%2Fs%2Fslim-belly-chain%2F6954316\u0026amp;subId1=___psv__p_49135775__t_w__r_www.popsugar.com%2Ffashion%2Fbandage-dress-trend-49446365_\u0026amp;subId3=product\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer sponsored\" aria-label=\"\" data-vars-action=\"product image\" data-vars-retailer=\"nordstrom\" data-vars-price=\"$75\" data-vars-href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/s/slim-belly-chain/6954316\"\u003e\u003cpicture data-testid=\"picture-tag\"\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/7RT_FvuCAjs6I9gp-aIOwgApgxY=/fit-in/516x516/filters:format_auto():extract_cover():upscale():fill(ffffff)/2025/06/09/757/n/1922564/75e0ede18e97160b_12cb0c41-533a-41d6-ac35-9a79cfbb40b9.jpeg\" media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-size=\"desktop\" width=\"258\" height=\"258\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/7RT_FvuCAjs6I9gp-aIOwgApgxY=/fit-in/516x516/filters:format_auto():extract_cover():upscale():fill(ffffff)/2025/06/09/757/n/1922564/75e0ede18e97160b_12cb0c41-533a-41d6-ac35-9a79cfbb40b9.jpeg\" media=\"(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px)\" data-size=\"tablet\" width=\"258\" height=\"258\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/-QwrA9UXJtwWcpjs7sEIEC8u1Rc=/fit-in/700x700/filters:format_auto():extract_cover():upscale():fill(ffffff)/2025/06/09/757/n/1922564/75e0ede18e97160b_12cb0c41-533a-41d6-ac35-9a79cfbb40b9.jpeg\" media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" data-size=\"mobile\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/jHAtTI8KwaZ3udJd3vk29ZWuDd8=/fit-in/350x350/filters:format_auto():quality(70):extract_cover():upscale():fill(ffffff)/2025/06/09/757/n/1922564/75e0ede18e97160b_12cb0c41-533a-41d6-ac35-9a79cfbb40b9.jpeg\" alt=\"Main Image\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135778\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"14\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eBieber styled a golden string bikini for her Rhode Passionfruit Jelly Peptide Lip Treatment photo shoot, released in April 2023.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135779\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"15\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eBieber\u0026#39;s Heavy Manners bikini, selected for her spring 2023 Rhode shoot, features tropical flowers against a lime-green background and a tie at the triangle bust.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135781\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"16\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eAnother one of Bieber\u0026#39;s Rhode bikinis was this golden-yellow bandeau styled with a belly chain, more acrylic bangles, a beaded choker necklace, hoops, and white bottoms.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135802\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"17\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eBieber\u0026#39;s vintage moment in Dior in April 2020.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135803\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"18\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eBieber paired her white bikini with a button-down, styled open as a cover-up. She finished the moment with a straw cowboy hat for some cabana shots in Jamaica in 2019.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135804\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"19\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eBieber styled a cheeky golden-yellow bikini with Nikes, also showing off her tiny hip tattoo, in 2020.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135806\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"20\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eBieber styled a white terry-cloth bikini with an oversize button-down, jewelry, and a velvet scrunchie while enjoying a cup of coffee poolside in 2019.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135808\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"21\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eNever one to shy away from a cheeky style, Bieber wore a pink floral two-piece to remind her followers to vote in September 2020.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135809\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"22\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eEnjoying a sun-kissed moment with husband Justin Bieber, Bieber styled a black two-piece underneath a blue linen button-down for a beach shot in 2020.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135810\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"23\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eBieber opted for a tie-dye set in 2021, posting a dump that also included a royal-blue and yellow bikini.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49135811\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"24\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eHailey Bieber Bikinis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-element-index=\"0\"\u003eBieber kept it classic in 2021, accessorizing her pink-and-yellow floral bikini with friend Kendall Jenner\u0026#39;s 818 Tequila.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"photo-49446892\" data-element-type=\"ParagraphSlide\" data-element-index=\"25\"\u003e\u003cfigure data-element-type=\"ParagraphImage\" data-element-index=\"0\"\u003e\u003cpicture data-testid=\"picture-tag\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/-305kbwMUI4OMXr0uQ4c32TRa_4=/fit-in/792x11/top/filters:format_auto():upscale()/2025/06/09/781/n/1922564/bd63596bf747e9a9_Commerce_Mini_Bio_Slides.png\" width=\"792\" height=\"11\" srcset=\"https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/-305kbwMUI4OMXr0uQ4c32TRa_4=/fit-in/792x11/top/filters:format_auto():upscale()/2025/06/09/781/n/1922564/bd63596bf747e9a9_Commerce_Mini_Bio_Slides.png 1000w, https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/17JGRfxBwhoP-u6sc8Kw9p23E84=/fit-in/1584x22/top/filters:format_auto():upscale()/2025/06/09/781/n/1922564/bd63596bf747e9a9_Commerce_Mini_Bio_Slides.png 2000w\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv data-element-type=\"ParagraphBodyText\" data-element-index=\"1\"\u003e\